query: computer science 2020 acl yujia qin erica improving entity and relation understanding for pre trained language models via contrastive learning
sql:
SELECT
    p.paper_id,
    p.title,
    p.abstract,
    p.venue,
    p.year,
    p.citation_count,
    p.open_access_url,
    STRING_AGG(a.name, ', ' ORDER BY pa.author_position) AS authors
FROM Papers p
JOIN PaperAuthors pa ON p.paper_id = pa.paper_id
JOIN Authors a ON pa.author_id = a.author_id
WHERE
    -- Year filter
    p.year = 2020
    -- Venue filter (ACL-related)
    AND (
        LOWER(p.venue) LIKE '%acl%'      -- ACL, ACL main, ACL anthology venues
        OR LOWER(p.venue) LIKE '%acl-%'  -- e.g., ACL-IJCNLP
    )
    -- Author filters
    AND EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM PaperAuthors pa2
        JOIN Authors a2 ON pa2.author_id = a2.author_id
        WHERE pa2.paper_id = p.paper_id
          AND LOWER(a2.name) LIKE '%yujia qin%'
    )
    AND EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM PaperAuthors pa3
        JOIN Authors a3 ON pa3.author_id = a3.author_id
        WHERE pa3.paper_id = p.paper_id
          AND LOWER(a3.name) LIKE '%erica%'
    )
    -- Title/abstract keyword filters (contrastive learning, entity, relation, pre-trained LM)
    AND (
        LOWER(p.title) LIKE '%contrastive%'
        OR LOWER(p.abstract) LIKE '%contrastive%'
    )
    AND (
        LOWER(p.title) LIKE '%entity%'
        OR LOWER(p.abstract) LIKE '%entity%'
    )
    AND (
        LOWER(p.title) LIKE '%relation%'
        OR LOWER(p.abstract) LIKE '%relation%'
    )
    AND (
        LOWER(p.title) LIKE '%pre-trained%'
        OR LOWER(p.abstract) LIKE '%pre-trained%'
        OR LOWER(p.title) LIKE '%pre trained%'
        OR LOWER(p.abstract) LIKE '%pre trained%'
    )
GROUP BY
    p.paper_id, p.title, p.abstract, p.venue, p.year, p.citation_count, p.open_access_url
